Package prng.utility

This package provides a collection of utility code.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BLOBPrint
    Utility functions for printing out binary data in a nice format.
    Config
    Configuration data.
    DigestDataOutput
    An output stream that only calculates a digest.
    NonceFactory
    A factory for nonces where 256-bit security is required.
    TimeBasedUUID
    Implementation of UUID generator that uses time/location based generation method (variant 1).
    UUIDTime
    Representation of the time and sequence used to generate Type-1 UUIDs.

Package prng.utility Description

This package provides a collection of utility code. Please see the individual classes for what they do and how they do it.

Simon Greatrix
